Module fi.tuni.prog3.sisu

Package fi.tuni.prog3.sisu

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    iAPI
    Interface for extracting data from the Sisu API.
    iReadAndWriteToFile
    Interface with methods to read from a file and write to a file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    A class defining a single course.
    DegreeModule
    An abstract class for DegreeProgram, StudyModule, and Course.
    DegreeProgram
    A class for representing Degree Program.
    ReadAndWriteStudentData
    A class implementing iReadAndWriteToFile.
    ReadAPI
    This class is responsible for reading the study related information from the Sisu API.
    Sisu
    JavaFX Sisu Reads the course data from sisu API, asks a new student to create account and choose a degree program, or an existing student to log in, and creates and updates the ui for the user student's course data.
    Student
    Class defining a student.
    StudyModule
    A class for representing StudyModule, extends the abstract class DegreeModule
